[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A care-coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: program enrollment with consent, longitudinal-store initialization with multi-source care-plan synthesis, channel entry with disclosure refresh, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading with care-plan-of-record retrieval, conversation handling with multi-source-grounded responses and cross-bot orchestration, output safety screening with companion-pattern detection, warm-handoff routing to the named care manager, multi-system task-completion reflection, and audit logging with care-coordination-specific retention discipline. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (multi-source care-plan-of-record integration as architectural primitive, cross-bot orchestration and routing as first-class architecture, program-specific protocol delivery with per-program governance, care-manager-workforce integration as primary architectural component, and SDOH-screening-and-resource-navigation as architectural primitive).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolled by care-management workflow]          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-manager-initiated (most common): the named      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      care manager identifies a patient appropriate for    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      bot-assisted coordination and initiates enrollment   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Payer-initiated: payer's care-management referral    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-initiated where program permits              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented program consent                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented bot-interaction consent                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Caregiver-participation consent (if applicable),     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      collected separately and revocable                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-organization-data-sharing consent (where       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      bot accesses data outside the institution)           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Privacy posture explained in plain language          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; enrollment              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    confirmation; named-care-manager assignment]           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE INITIALIZATION ─────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Multi-source care-plan synthesis]                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - EHR: problem list, medication list, allergy list,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      recent encounters                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-management platform: active care plan, goals,   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      tasks, care-manager assignments, recent CM notes     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduling system(s): upcoming appointments across   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      all integrated scheduling sources                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral-tracking system: open referrals and status  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Quality-measure data source: open care gaps          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient-engagement platform: prior bot interactions, │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      stated preferences                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SDOH-resource directory: institutional and           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      community resources for the patient's geography      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - External integrations: specialty pharmacy, DME       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      vendor, home-health agency, payer eligibility,       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      community organizations (per consent and per         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      data-sharing agreement)                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Source-of-truth annotation]                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Each data element tagged with its source system,     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      its update timestamp, its trust level, and its       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conflict-resolution rule                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-plan synthesized view: cached, refreshed per    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation or per upstream-event trigger           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent-context summary: separately maintained        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history: S3 with vector retrieval       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for coordination      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    conversations]                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
