[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY WITH DISCLOSURE ─────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-initiated entry]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - In-app chat (most common in mature deployments)      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS                                                  │
