[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      appointment confirmation)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-manager-requested between-visit check-ins       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - All initiation respects patient quiet hours,         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      channel preferences, and contact-frequency limits    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disclosure refresh per session or per defined cadence] │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm a chat tool that works with your care team"     │
