[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard input safety primitives from recipe 11.1]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    313[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHI minimization                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    316[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Continuous emergency screening]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute clinical-symptom emergency (chest pain,        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      sudden weakness, severe shortness of breath, severe  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    319[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      bleeding, anaphylaxis, sudden severe headache, etc.) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    320[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mental-health crisis (any self-harm or suicidal      │
