[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    542[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: durable, multi-system reflection of patient    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    543[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    self-reported task completion]                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    544[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
