[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    550[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - User utterances                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    551[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Tool calls with arguments and results                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    552[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Generated bot responses                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    553[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-bot orchestration events                       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    554[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active model and prompt versions                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    555[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active protocol-corpus version                       │
