[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    557[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Final disposition                                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    558[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    559[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Care-coordination-specific retention]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    560[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Retention sized to longest of HIPAA's six-year       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    561[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      minimum, state-specific care-management-record       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    562[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      retention rules, accreditation-body retention        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    563[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      requirements (NCQA, URAC), payer-contract retention  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    564[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      requirements, and litigation-hold obligations        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    565[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    566[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Outcome correlation as multi-quarter to multi-year     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    567[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    commitment]                                            │
