[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    579[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Operational telemetry]                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    580[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Engagement rate by patient cohort                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    581[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Attrition rate by patient cohort                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    582[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Task-completion rate (overall and by task type)      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    583[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appointment-attendance rate                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    584[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral-completion rate                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    585[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-gap-closure rate                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    586[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Warm-handoff completion rate                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    587[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Cross-bot-routing accuracy                           │
